Ascape/R interface classes.

Class Summary
AscapeGD An R graphics device in the Ascape Swing MDI.
PanelViewDatasetProvider Fetches the dataset for run 0 from a OutputDatasetProvider each time PanelViewDatasetProvider.getPanelView() is called.
PanelViewRTextCommand Executes an command in R each time PanelViewRTextCommand.getPanelView() is called.
RFileInterface Handles the opening, display, execution and saving of R files in the GUI.
ScapeRInterface Exposes scape specific R functionality for a particular scape, as well as general R functionality.
ScapeRListener R related operations performed on scape events.
 

Enum Summary
